thread.title: BRIEF-India's City Union Bank Dec-Qtr Profit Up About 22 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's City Union Bank Dec-Qtr Profit Up About 22 Pct
text:
Feb 7 (Reuters) - City Union Bank Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT 1.55 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT OF 1.27 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 8.65 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 8.11 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS 856.6 MILLION RUPEES VERSUS 919.6 MILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 3.30 PERCENT VERSUS 3.07 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 1.74 PERCENT VERSUS 1.76 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text: bit.ly/2sdScSL Further company coverage:
